class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Waste of Money / Doesn&#039;t work</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jayeltee\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/787bce84a584d51e66cf57b67fed4824?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/787bce84a584d51e66cf57b67fed4824?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jayeltee\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jayeltee</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 10, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have literally just signed up to be able to leave this review. My company\'s site\'s average loading speed had been steadily decreasing every month leading up to purchasing a paid subscription to Optimole in April this year. Now without fail the average loading speed has become slower each month using Optimole.\n\nI have cancelled our subscription today as your service literally does the opposite of what we were paying you to do.\n\nAccording to all your stats on your site and in the optimole media section in WP your service was supposedly making our photos way smaller, but without anything being added to our site apart from Optimole we now have lower loading speeds. Something doesn\'t add up.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">