	</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tommalcolm\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/eb3e89b094ca8217f5dee4dfb6fc1e38?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/eb3e89b094ca8217f5dee4dfb6fc1e38?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tommalcolm\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tommalcolm</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 4, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Great combination of features, easy to tweak and does what it\'s supposed to do. All that plus great support!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Great!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dzsatria\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/431d32b42e11d7aa8bc9be3855b1d16e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/431d32b42e11d7aa8bc9be3855b1d16e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dzsatria\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dzsatria</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 28, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Works like a charm !</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Much better than Imagify</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/helixnetworks\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6580b064ee5930abee707c5495140be2?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/6580b064ee5930abee707c5495140be2?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/helixnetworks\" class=\"reviewer-name\">helixnetworks</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 25, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve tried a few plugins, but this one was much better and cleaner. I\'m quite impressed and happy!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome Plugin.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mynameisrabby\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5ca988df7897ea786e45dc8d15425160?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5ca988df7897ea786e45dc8d15425160?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mynameisrabby\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Mahmudul H. Rabby <small>(mynameisrabby)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 21, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">WOW. It\'s an awesome plugin. Very helpful, easy to use. The free version is very good.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Five Stars!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cristianltn\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f72e9e49fb093b5b85415e2de1f4bf68?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f72e9e49fb093b5b85415e2de1f4bf68?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cristianltn\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cristianltn</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 19, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Excellent work!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good and getting better all the time</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/martingfisher\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/95058c568eaea3b7b19639b8378ce032?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/95058c568eaea3b7b19639b8378ce032?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/martingfisher\" class=\"reviewer-name\">martingfisher</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 17, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Seems quick and I love the way it yields correct WEBP images so easily and \nReally interested to see how this grows. I can see it attracting lots of users of small sites but that won\'t help Optimoles revenue. Larger sites may well decide to go with people like key CDN who have launched their image CDN that works alongside their standard CDN. Optimole is a Solid product though - I wish them well</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">The best Compression</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/imatiler\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0e1a80939d0b8e3dfc351b5339b44ce8?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/0e1a80939d0b8e3dfc351b5339b44ce8?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/imatiler\" class=\"reviewer-name\">imatiler</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 14, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The heading says everything you need to know.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:98:\"Improve your site loading speed by delivering optimized image for each device. Lazy load included.\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:54:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/optimole-wp.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:4:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-1.jpeg?rev=1991524\";s:7:\"caption\";s:14:\"Welcome screen\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-2.jpeg?rev=1991521\";s:7:\"caption\";s:14:\"Connect screen\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-3.jpeg?rev=1991521\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"Plugin dashboard\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/optimole-wp/assets/screenshot-4.jpe