w-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Thanks</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/duveit\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e406193a2aa7cc79d5e65a923c8bc2c5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e406193a2aa7cc79d5e65a923c8bc2c5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/duveit\" class=\"reviewer-name\">duveit</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 31, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Everything works well, thank you ;o)</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:159:\"Create beautiful and attracting posts, pages, and landing pages with Gutenberg Blocks and Template Library by Otter. Otter comes with dozens of Gutenb &hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:55:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/otter-blocks.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:4:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-1.png?rev=2019293\";s:7:\"caption\";s:12:\"Otter Blocks\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-2.png?rev=2019293\";s:7:\"caption\";s:13:\"Section Block\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/screenshot-3.png?rev=2046920\";s:7:\"caption\";s:16:\"Template Library\";}i:4;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:65:\"https://ps.w.org/otter-blocks/assets/scree