id&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/sxperm\" class=\"reviewer-name\"> <small>(Sxperm)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 15, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin has a lot of good reviews and rating features.  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Nice Plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/grayson9\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/95e8fb0c1a45308475aa3677c2e55689?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/95e8fb0c1a45308475aa3677c2e55689?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/grayson9\" class=\"reviewer-name\">grayson9</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 10, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">A great little plugin that worked for me straight out of the box. In fact, I thought my GTmetrix score improved but it could have been a fluke. I accept the fluke all the same.\nThe plugin could do with a little more information in the product fields like maybe just a simple page review score. \nAs an example, I don\'t actually have any products and my services are not noted so I am cheating the plugin a bit.\n\nBut very satisfied and my page is prettier. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Does not work | не работает как надо</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"2 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"2\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/andrews32\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4fe770f4dd7fc277cdc35ba530d85ed9?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/4fe770f4dd7fc277cdc35ba530d85ed9?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/andrews32\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Andrews32</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 20, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Just after installing, the admin dashboard does not work (any admin page). The only phrase displays:\n\nFatal error: Call to undefined function ThemeisleSDK\\Modules\\get_user_locale() in /wp-content/plugins/wp-product-review/vendor/codeinwp/themeisle-sdk/src/Modules/Translate.php on line 786.\n\nchanged “return get_user_locale();” to “return true;” and the plugin (and site dashboard) started to work again.\n\nAlso, the review form (“write a review”) does not appear on the pages after adding the [P_REVIEW] shortcode. Deactivated &amp; uninstalled.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good plugin</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/manoaratefy\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9e9046b130db2152ab592055cc0a0f1d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9e9046b130db2152ab592055cc0a0f1d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/manoaratefy\" class=\"reviewer-name\">manoaratefy</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 7, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I made a review website with this plugin, without issue.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">good</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div