d bugs (would love to turn off the auto-population feature, have to put the $ sign in front of prices, etc.) but on the whole it\'s a nice little plug-in. Also Google admin tool is kicking out some error messages, but the creator says they are working on this...</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Easy to Use</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nudge1969\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a116240b3b7e68cf8c11a25d40a928db?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a116240b3b7e68cf8c11a25d40a928db?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/nudge1969\" class=\"reviewer-name\">nudge1969</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">March 28, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Really enjoying this product, does exactly as stated. Just getting a few errors on Google Search Console but I here that will be cleared up in the next update.</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:53:\"将您的基础性文章变成带有评价、&hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:60:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/wp-product-review.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:7:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:69:\"https://ps.w.org/wp-product-review/trunk/screenshot-1.png?rev