me\">Fotis Pastrakis <small>(fotisps)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 24, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The whole plugin is great. Visual editor saves a lot of time when translating new strings! Easy to use without any glitches on the actual page when it\'s translated. Keep it up!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">The Best</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/giulyman24\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fbd3f23e54aff69e7dbc5d45972e9422?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/fbd3f23e54aff69e7dbc5d45972e9422?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/giulyman24\" class=\"reviewer-name\">giulyman24</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 21, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Après avoir essayé WPML, qtranslateX et transpoch rien ne marchait correctement sans créer de bug dans mon site, Weglot est absolument parfait et simplisme à utiliser ! </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Intelligent service, very recommended!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/faradistravel\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/94b8f97bd5f6ddd91a6bc89871d4761e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/94b8f97bd5f6ddd91a6bc89871d4761e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/faradistravel\" class=\"reviewer-name\">faradistravel</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">June 20, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'m very grateful to Weglot team they are the best, the translation tool is very smart my website were professionally translated to several languages in a minute, I could also edit translations the way I want. It\'s great I already started to received visits on my translated pages. \nthinking about translating your website? write Weglot team!</div>\n</div>\n\";}s:17:\"short_description\";s:23:\"Translate your &hellip;\";s:13:\"download_link\";s:55:\"https://downloads.wordpress.org/plugin/weglot.3.0.6.zip\";s:11:\"screenshots\";a:4:{i:1;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:59:\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-1.jpg?rev=2009075\";s:7:\"caption\";s:52:\"Example on front end: language switch button on page\";}i:2;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s:59:\"https://ps.w.org/weglot/assets/screenshot-2.jpg?rev=2009083\";s:7:\"caption\";s:30:\"Weglot Translate settings page\";}i:3;a:2:{s:3:\"src\";s: